question: What about some ShinKami headcanons?
answer:
one of the many sunshine/emo ships, it’s a good ‘un

  • Pokémon go dates! They don’t care it’s not cool anymore
  • also it’s practically the only time Shinso gets fresh air
  • they are both Real Sleepy most of the time so they nap together
  • but not like, in their dorms just around
  • Canteen, library, in class, you name it
  • It’s not all that unusual to see them sitting on a windowsill just snoozin
  • Denki is rEally clingy and maybe low key touch starved so he always has his arms around Shinso
  • Kinda like a sloth
  • It’s Shinso’s fault for being really warm tbh
  • Shinso absolutely does Not use his quirk on Kami period.
  • Well, only in life threatening situations, like if Kaminari’s quirk went berserk (as I hc it sometimes does)
  • As soon as Shinso joined 1a he instantly became a member of the Bakusquad and the Choker Gang (Kami and Jiro)
  • He wears a choker with his hero suit now
  • They prolly have charm bracelets or something like that
  • No, those rubber wristbands! Super edgy ones
  • People who say Kami isn’t emo…

blog.title: Fake texts from last Might
blog.description: Things BNHA characters most definitely never said (sadly).

summary: Bakugou Katsuki : "Don't be so mean to Deku", "Apologize to Deku", Deku this, Deku that... urgh, it's like everyone wants to...
body:
Bakugou Katsuki : "Don't be so mean to Deku", "Apologize to Deku", Deku this, Deku that... urgh, it's like everyone wants to change me! Motorboy, Floaty, Sparkles, Frogger, that Half-and-half bastard...
Kirishima Eijirou : Oh, don't be ridiculous, Bakugou. You make it sound like everyone's out to get you.
Kirishima Eijirou : [whispering to his cellphone] Your holiness, subject #0475 is compromized. Possibly becoming sentient. Shall I use sex to distract him?
Midoriya Inko : [through cellphone] No, Agent Red. We'll just have All for One kidnap him. Leak the location of the training camp. Tell Dabi to incinerate him. By the time rescue arrives, we'll have him replaced with clone #0476.
Kirishima Eijirou : [whispering] At once, your holiness. Soon, EVERYONE shall be Izuku's friend!
